      "created": 1777024111,
      "updated": 1777024111
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb3c6f00000000009b8db6",
      "text": ">34 ななしのよっしん",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777024111,
      "updated": 1777024113
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb3c7000000000009b8db7",
      "text": "> 2021/05/19(水) 13:29:17 ID: lFjpOkELTJ",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777024113,
      "updated": 1777024113
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb3c7000000000009b8db9",
      "text": "> セリフをリズムとして解釈してビートを乗せる音MADの発展のようなスタイル",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777024113,
      "updated": 1777024128
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb3c7000000000009b8dba",
      "text": "> セリフをメロディとして解釈してハーモニーやコードをつけるスタイル",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777024113,
      "updated": 1777024126
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb3c7000000000009b8dbb",
      "text": "> それぞれ分けて考えたほうが分類も理解も楽だと思われる",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777024113,
      "updated": 1777024124
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb3bce00000000009b8da7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777023951,
      "updated": 1777023951
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb3c1000000000009b8dab",
      "text": "この技法を多数手がけた人物としては[2÷す]氏が有名",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777024017,
      "updated": 1777024156
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb3d4a00000000009b8dc7",
      "text": " [GIRL'∫ 綴RHYTHM]",
